      desc 'barrage is a point and click tank game.
Your goal is to kill and destroy
as many targets as possible within 3 minutes.
You control a gun which may fire either small
or large grenades by point-and-click at
soldiers, jeeps, and tanks, and which must
be reloaded from time to time.'
